quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  41,12,"O timminiri …ói kammuuji jee…ói…ói ndeer bal…óe …ói…ói, O yamiri kala kammu, fiyaaku maggu. Min cu…óiniri kammu aduna ngun, koode e reenir…óum. ∆äum ko e…ď…ďoore poolu…óo, ganndu…óo On."
  41,13,"Si …ďe …óuurnike, haray wi'u …ďe: "Min nejertinirii on haacaangu, sugu ha'acaango Aadi'en e Samuuda'en."
  41,14,"nde Nulaa…ďe …ďren ardirannoo…ďe, ye'eso ma…ď…ďe e …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe, won'de: "Wata on ndewu dey, si wonaa Allah", …ďe mb'i: "Si Joomi amen haajuno, ko Malaa'ika O jippinaynoo. Awa minen, ko min yeddu…ďe ko nula…óon mum kon"."
  41,15,"Aadii'en kan, …ďe mawnintini ka hoore leydi, ko aldaa e goonga, …ďe mbi'i: "Hara ko hommbo …ďuri min doole?" E …ďee yiaani, won'de Allah tak…óo …ďe On no …ďuri …ďe tii…óude doole? ∆Āe ngoni e yeddugol Aayeeje amen …óen."
  41,16,"Min ngurti henndu …ďuu…ďundu e ma…ď…ďe e √Īalaa…óe hiitaa…óe, fii no Min mee…óinira …ďe lepte koyeera …óen ka nguurndam aduna. Pellet, ko lepte La'akara …óen …ďuri won'de koyeera, kadi …ďe faaboytaake."
  41,17,"Samuuda'en kan, Min …ďannginanno …ďe; kono …ďe su…ďii bum…óam …óam e dow peewal ngal. Dillere lepte hoynooje …óen nanngiri …ďe, sabu ko …ďe paggitotonoo kon."
  41,18,"Min nda…óndi gooŇč…óim…ďe …ďe woniina hulnoo…ďe …ďen."
  41,19,"√Ďalnde noon ay√Ī…ďe Allah …ďeen moo…ďiroytee faade ka Yiite... Hara he…ďe √Īo∆ī∆īindiree."
  41,20,"Haa si …ďe hewtii nge, nann…óe ma…ď…ďe …óeen, e gii…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, e guri …ďalli ma…ď…ďe …óin seeditoo e dow ma…ď…ďe, kon ko …ďe gollatnoo."